                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "id": "68f8d39",
                      "elType": "widget",
                      "settings": {
                        "editor": "<p class=\"\" data-start=\"980\" data-end=\"1205\">But Eric didn’t stop there. To educate farmers, he began building a <strong data-start=\"1109\" data-end=\"1141\">10,000-plant Vetiver nursery</strong>, forming a live training hub for agroecological transformation.</p><p class=\"\" data-start=\"1210\" data-end=\"1377\">Working with a major agricultural group, Eric continues to advocate for systemic change, backed not by speeches, but by <strong data-start=\"1330\" data-end=\"1351\">actionable models</strong> other farmers can follow.</p>"
                      },
