                        "editor": "<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">In just one growing season:</p><ul><li>Soil erosion dropped by 90%</li><li>Crop yields increased by 40%</li><li>Additional income streams emerged </li><li>Zero need for new land clearing</li></ul>"
