                      "id": "097de0f",
                      "elType": "widget",
                      "settings": {
                        "editor": "<p><em><strong>\"Before Vetiver, I burned my land every season, watching my soil disappear. Now, my children will inherit fertile ground, not ashes.\"</strong></em></p><p>Eric’s work spans across the Congo, with active projects in:</p><ul><li>Kongo Central (2 sites)</li><li>Mongala (2 sites)</li><li>Équateur (2 sites)</li><li>Tshopo (1 site)</li><li>Tshuapa (1 site)</li></ul><p>This network is creating a living ecosystem of resilience across the country.</p>",
