                      "id": "5b66f51",
                      "elType": "widget",
                      "settings": {
                        "editor": "<p> </p><p class=\"\" data-start=\"1982\" data-end=\"2007\">Your donation helps fund:</p><ul data-start=\"2010\" data-end=\"2128\"><li class=\"\" data-start=\"2010\" data-end=\"2041\"><p class=\"\" data-start=\"2012\" data-end=\"2041\">Vetiver nurseries for farmers</p></li><li class=\"\" data-start=\"2044\" data-end=\"2083\"><p class=\"\" data-start=\"2046\" data-end=\"2083\">Local training with Eric’s board game</p></li><li class=\"\" data-start=\"2086\" data-end=\"2126\"><p class=\"\" data-start=\"2088\" data-end=\"2126\">Tools and supplies for new communities</p></li></ul><p class=\"\" data-start=\"2131\" data-end=\"2223\"><strong data-start=\"2131\" data-end=\"2173\">Donate today and grow a greener Congo.</strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Join us in creating a sustainable future. Whether you're a:</span></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Farmer seeking solutions</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Organization looking to partner</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Donor ready to make an impact</li><li>Your contribution matters. Start today.</li></ul><p>▶ <a href=\"https://vetiversansfrontieres.org/get-involved/\">Start Your Project</a><br />▶ <a href=\"https://vetiversansfrontieres.org/get-involved/\">Make a Donation</a><br />▶ <a href=\"https://vetiversansfrontieres.org/about/vetiver-system/\">Learn More</a></p><p>Contact us  to begin your journey toward soil regeneration.</p>"
